"     Patient information: Alcohol use &mdash; when is drinking a problem? (The Basics)",
"    </div>",
"    <span class=\"view\">",
"     View in",
"     <a class=\"lang\" href=\"./es-419/alcohol-use-when-is-drinking-a-problem-the-basics?source=topic_page\">",
